h2.Workaround
No work around unfortunately but problem is being looked at by Innovalog.

Atlassian connect add-on users are currently counting toward the JIRA Software license. This is causing instances to exceed the license count and become non-functional. The following message appears across the top of the JIRA UI:

{quote}
Your JIRA Software license's user limit is exceeded. Users with this license only can't create issues until you have upgraded your license or reduced the number of users.
{quote}

*Workaround*

Please log a ticket with Atlassian Support at https://support.atlassian.com, we will increase your user limit temporarily to workaround the problem until we can solve it.

